reviews.review_text: Very, very kind Scarlet Jerry Meandering Jam... This is one of the best Jerry Scarlet Beg. jam I've ever heard. Very mellow and intertwined with melodic brilliance. Kind stuff.

Starts out as a crappy audience then goes into crystal board I think this is the playin fromm steal your face though not that sure. This is as good as this board gets problem is 1974 is filled with shows like this.... Phil & Ned (40 mins of cacophony) take what was a good show into a free form and pretty tedious long jam.
